content: Data import from Nextcloud to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} is complete!

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a success message after completing data import from Nextcloud to an organization. It appears in the UI as a confirmation message, typically on a button or dialog that indicates successful import completion.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'Входиране' (Vhodirane) is not the most natural or accurate translation of 'import' in this context. It implies entering or inputting data, rather than a data migration process.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Прехвърлянето на данни от Nextcloud към {{organizationName}} {{productName}} е завършено!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation is not ideal. While technically correct, 'Import dat z Nextcloudu' sounds somewhat awkward. A more natural phrasing would be 'Import dat z Nextcloudu do...' or 'Přenášení dat z Nextcloudu...'
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Přenášení dat z Nextcloudu do {{organizationName}} {{productName}} je dokončeno!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Greek translation places 'του' between 'Nextcloud' and '{{productName}}'. This disrupts the flow and might not be the most natural phrasing. While grammatically correct, consider if a simpler construction is preferred.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Nextcloud στο {{productName}} του {{organizationName}} ολοκληρώθηκε!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The colon and space after 'Nextcloudista' creates an awkward phrasing. It's better to integrate the organization and product names more smoothly.

The phrase "ավարտված է" (avartvady e) literally translates to 'is finished' which is correct but slightly less natural in this context. A more natural phrasing would convey completion in a proactive way.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nextcloud-ից տվյալների ներմուծումը {{organizationName}} {{productName}}-ի մեջ ավարտվել է:

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Nextcloud에서 {{organizationName}} {{productName}}로 데이터 가져오기가 완료되었습니다!' is technically correct but could be more natural and concise. The phrase '로 데이터 가져오기가 완료되었습니다!' (to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} data import is complete!) feels a little clunky in Korean. It's more common to say something like '에 데이터 가져오기가 완료되었습니다!' (to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} data import is complete!) or to restructure the sentence.
The word 'importação' should be 'importação de dados'. While technically correct, the added 'de dados' makes it more explicit and natural-sounding in Portuguese.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação de dados do Nextcloud para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} está concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'importação' should be capitalized at the beginning of the sentence.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A Importação de dados do Nextcloud para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} está concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Import date din Nextcloud în {{organizationName}} {{productName}} este finalizat!" uses 'date' which translates to 'date' in English. It should be 'Importul'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Importul de date din Nextcloud în {{organizationName}} {{productName}} este finalizat!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Serbian translation 'Увоз података са Nextcloud на {{organizationName}} {{productName}} је завршен!' translates literally as 'Import of data from Nextcloud to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} is complete!'. A more natural and idiomatic translation would be 'Пренос података са Nextcloud на {{organizationName}} {{productName}} је завршен!' (Transfer of data...).  'Увоз' often implies importing from an external source in a more complex, potentially problematic manner.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Пренос података са Nextcloud на {{organizationName}} {{productName}} је завршен!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of "Nextcloud" should be "Nextcloud" instead of "工作区" (workspace). While technically understandable, it's better to retain the original name for clarity and consistency.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 从 Nextcloud 到 {{organizationName}}{{productName}}的数据导入已完成！
